              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Error of MISC1."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Of authors. Antimony sample was activated in the",
                "irradiation hole of JRR-3.No irradiation covered with",
                "cadmium was carried out. Obtained result gives the",
                "reactor neutron capture cross section, that is not",
                "thermal but effective (including epithermal) neutron",
                "capture cross section. It is  therefore considered that",
                "the present cross section value is a maximum value for",
                "the thermal neutron capture cross section of Sb-124."
              ]
            }
